gomodel:SYNGO_2179  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.4: \"Consistent with the finding that the IPSPs elicited by bitufted dendrite-preferring cells were insensitive to the α1/2/3 subunit-selective agonist, zolpidem (Figs 2C,E and 4Ab), these IPSPs were sensitive to IAalpha5 (1 μM, Fig. 4Ab,Bb,C)\"\n\nFig.5: \"This indicates a predominantly postsynaptic site for the changes in IPSP amplitude with bath application of zolpidem, IAalpha5, or zinc.\". Experimental description: \"Synaptic α5 Subunit-Containing GABAA Receptors Mediate IPSPs Elicited by Dendrite-Preferring Cells in Rat Neocortex\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0593-3443" ;
